tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE cash_flow_tracking (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transaction_date DATE,
    amount DECIMAL,
    description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    opening_balance DECIMAL,
    closing_balance DECIMAL,
    cash_inflow DECIMAL,
    cash_outflow DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE CashFlow (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transaction_date DATE,
    amount DECIMAL(10,2),
    category VARCHAR(50),
    notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Liquidity (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    current_balance DECIMAL(10,2),
    cash_inflow DECIMAL(10,2),
    cash_outflow DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE FinancialData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    account_name VARCHAR(50),
    income DECIMAL(10,2),
    expenses DECIMAL(10,2),
    balance DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE cash_flows (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    amount DECIMAL,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(255),
    transaction_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE liquidity (
    liquidity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    liquidity_amount DECIMAL,
    time_stamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    company_name VARCHAR(255),
    revenue DECIMAL,
    expenses DECIMAL,
    profit DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE financial_transactions (
    transact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transact_type VARCHAR(255),
    transact_amount DECIMAL,
    transact_date DATE
)
